sources.description:
If you go down to the woods today - you might never get out alive!
A cannibal hermit living in the woods preys on campers and hikers for his food supply. 

Original title: The Forest (1982) AKA: Terror in the Forest


This film has English and French audio options, and is subtitled in many languages.


Director: Don Jones 
Writer: Don Jones (as Evan Jones) 
Stars: Dean Russell, Gary Kent, Tomi Barrett, John Batis
Genre: Cult Movies, Horror, Thriller
